<% if @for_self %>
  You have earned a CoughDrop badge!
<% else %>
  <%= @user.user_name %> has earned a CoughDrop badge!
<% end %>
<br/><br/>
<% if @badge.data['image_url'] %>
  <div style='max-width: 200px; margin: 0 auto; text-align: center; font-size: 2em;'>
    <img src='<%= @badge.data['image_url'] %>' style='max-width: 200px;' alt='badge' /><br/>
    <strong><%= @badge.data['name'] %></strong><br/>
    <span style='font-size: 1.5em;'>Level <%= @badge.level %></span>
  </div>
<% else %>
  <h3><%= @badge.data['name'] %>, Level <%= @badge.level %></h3>
<% end %>
<br/><br/>
<% if @badge.data['global_goal'] %>
  As CoughDrop tracks your usage, you'll automatically see badges like this
  one awarded based on how much you use different features in CoughDrop, and
  what your typical usage looks like.
<% elsif @goal %>
  This badge is part of the goal, 
  <a href="<%= JsonApi::Json.current_host %>/<%= @user.user_name %>/goals/<%= @goal.global_id %>"><%= @goal.settings['summary'] %></a>, and
  you can see more detailed information on goal progress in the CoughDrop app.
<% end %>
<% if !@badge.data['max_level'] %>This badge is part of a set, so keep at it and see if you can move up to the next level!<% end %>
<br/><br/>
<% if @badge.global %>
  <span style='font-size: 0.8em;'>Did you know you can create your own badges in CoughDrop? Go to the "Goals" section of a user's account and you can set personalized goals, track them, and even build badges they can earn as they make progress on the goal!</span>
  <br/><br/>
<% end %>
Thanks!<br/>
- The CoughDrop Team
